  Locus:
    Date: 20 August 2017
    Chapter: 43
  Copyright: 2002
  Translator: Douglas Allchin
---
Water, ever fluid,
erodes the most resistant rock.
While what is insubstantial
penetrates the densest block.
Without ado,
non-action demonstrates what it can do.

Wisdom without words,
deeds without doing
are realized by very few.
